Definition: a focus of public attention
Example: he enjoyed being in the limelight; when Congress investigates it brings the full glare of publicity to the agency
Synonyms: spotlight, verb, change, glare, public_eye, prominence, a, focus, of, public, attention, he, enjoyed, being, in, the, when, Congress, investigates, it, brings, full, publicity, to, agency
Category: noun.state
